        <div name="LinReal" style="display: none">
          <h3>2.2 Real installation using Linux</h3>
          While your watch is in fastboot bootloader mode, flash the userdata partition:
          <pre><code class="bash">fastboot flash userdata ~/Downloads/asteroid-image-{{deviceNames.[0]}}.{{#if simg}}simg{{else}}ext4{{/if}}</code></pre>
          And the boot partition:
          <pre><code class="bash">fastboot flash boot ~/Downloads/zImage-dtb-{{deviceNames.[0]}}.fastboot</code></pre>
          Then continue the boot process:
          <pre><code class="bash">fastboot continue</code></pre>
        </div>

